  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Service Project Engineer",
  "description": "<p>For more than 100 years, the globally active SAUTER Group, with its headquarters and a development, logistics and marketing site in Basel (Switzerland) as well as a production site in Freiburg (Germany), has provided products, expertise and solutions for building management and room automation over the entire building life cycle.</p><p>We are looking for engineers to join our organization here in Singapore to expand our offering by utilizing the latest IOT technology for the Green Environment.</p><h3><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></h3><p><strong>Roles & Responsibility  for Assistant Service Engineer / Service Engineers:</strong></p><ul><li>Good interpersonal skills and ability to build customer’s relationship and satisfaction.</li></ul><ul><li>Dynamic and self-motivated individual who is independent and is able to work with a team</li></ul><ul><li>Willingness to learn </li></ul><ul><li>Ability to maintain, troubleshoot and repair Building Management  Control System & Laboratory control system</li></ul><ul><li>Ensuring smooth operation and reliability of systems</li></ul><ul><li>Supporting engineering tasks and site requirements</li></ul><ul><li>To plan and carry out preventive & corrective maintenance work</li></ul><ul><li>To plan, engineer, coordinate, implement and test service projects with sub-contractors and customers to deliver quality system.</li></ul><ul><li>Strong technical knowledge on Building Monitoring & Control, HVAC Controls, Programming and IT knowledge</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications & Experience :</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate must possess at least Bachelor's Degree/Post Graduate Diploma/Professional Degree in Engineering (Electrical/Electronic) or equivalent.</li></ul><ul><li>At least 2 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position. Fresh graduates may also apply</li></ul><ul><li>Required Skill(s): Proficient with use of MS Office, MS Project & Autocad. Knowledge of BIM is an added advantage   </li><li>Experience with Building Management System and good control philosophy is also added advantage</li></ul><ul><li>Experience for GMP validation is an added advantage</li></ul><ul><li>Only Singaporean or PR will be considered.</li></ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 2,
